In Command Mode
	:q			quit
	:w			save
	:q!			quit without savings
	:wq			quit and save
	:set number		set numbers on the left side
	i			change to insert mode
	Esc			change back to command mode
	ddd			delete current line
	3ddd			delete 3 lines (current and follow 2)
	u			undo
	Ctrl-r			redo
	/search_string		search, n for next and shift-n previous
	:%s/xx/yy		search and replace xx with yy (lazy)
	:%s/xx/yy/g		search and replace xx with yy (greedy)
	:%s/xx/yy/c		ask for confirmation	
